IN RE the MARRIAGE OF Christine Y. Freudenberg and Mark William FREUDENBERG Upon the Petition of Christine Y. Freudenberg, Petitioner-Appellant/Cross-Appellee, And Concerning Mark William Freudenberg, Respondent-Appellee/Cross-Appellant. No. 17-1569 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed December 5, 2018

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

Christine Freudenberg appeals, and Mark Freudenberg cross-appeals, a decree of dissolution of marriage. AFFIRMED AS MODIFIED.

AFFIRMED AS MODIFIED.
